To install CHIPIPE follow these steps:

1. Download the zip file CHIPIPE.zip to a directory of your choice. The opt directory is recommended.

2. Unzip the file:
	unzip CHIPIPE.zip

3. Edit your .bashrc file to add the CHIPIPE path to PATH:
	Open a terminal Ctrl+Alt*t
	cd
	vim .bashrc or nano .bashrc or gedit .bashrc
	add to the end of the file the CHIPIPE Path
	PATH=$PATH:CHIPIPE_PATH
